Package: DrugDataCoding
Title: Functions for Coding Drug-Related ICD-10 Codes in Claims and Death Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jay",
           family = "Unick",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "junick@ssw.umaryland.edu")
Description: This package provides functions for processing and coding drug-related 
    ICD-10 codes in healthcare claims data and mortality records. It includes 
    functions for identifying drug overdoses, specific substance use disorders, 
    and poisonings by drug category in accordance with CDC definitions. The package 
    is based on established coding practices from the National Center for Health 
    Statistics (NCHS).
